    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 remains in peak mechanical health, delivering linear power delivery through its 8,400 RPM redline. Equipped with the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission, gear changes are instantaneous, synchronized with a perfectly calibrated M Variable Differential Lock for optimal longitudinal traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing precise rebound and compression characteristics. Meticulously serviced with a comprehensive history, including proactive rod bearing verification and a flawless subframe inspection. A collector-grade specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
