    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example of automotive preservation. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one and shows as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a full-body paint protection film (PPF) and a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The alloy wheels are flawless, with no curb rash, and are wrapped in brand-new high-performance tires. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition\u2014the premium leather retains its original matte finish and firm bolsters, free of any creasing or wear. It has never been smoked in and has been kept in a pet-free environment, preserving that distinct 'new car' scent. Every electronic feature, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history exclusively from authorized dealerships. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, reflecting the mechanical care this vehicle has received. This is a turnkey opportunity for a collector or enthusiast seeking perfection.",
